titles.title: To clarify the boundaries of Coastal Barrier Resources System Clam Pass Unit FL-64P.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Resources.
Referred to the Subcommittee on Fisheries and Oceans.
Subcommittee on Fisheries and Oceans Discharged.
Committee Consideration and Mark-up Session Held.

calendar.text: Ordered to be Reported by Unanimous Consent.

action.text: Reported by the Committee on Resources. H. Rept. 109-581.

calendar.text: Placed on the Union Calendar, Calendar No. 333.

bill.summary: 7/20/2006--Reported to House without amendment. Replaces the map subtitled "FL-64P," relating to the Coastal Barrier Resources System unit designated as Coastal Barrier Resources System Clam Pass Unit FL-64P, that is included in the set of maps entitled "Coastal Barrier Resources System" and referred to in the Coastal Barrier Resources Act, with another map relating to that unit entitled "Coastal Barrier Resources System Clam Pass Unit, FL-64P", and dated July 21, 2005.
